       Dio is a native PHP library for generating ODF document.



About the name :
————————————————

Dio means God in esporanto

GOD means « Générateur d'OpenDocument » in french.



Status :
————————

 * Archive and Flat format implemented

 * Minimal spreadsheet generation implemented.


Design :
————————

Unlike OpenDocumentPHP ( http://opendocumentphp.org/ ), it has been
design with PHP rules, not Java ones.

It aims at providing document generation for all OpenDocument format
both as Zip archive or flat XML file.
